{"tid":2125973,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"24小時內，無官出嚟舉證辟謠的話，即認證以下描述的是事實囉。 作者：王喜","createTime":"2020-07-26T14:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T15:37:41.000Z","uid":285195,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"385c6b4b5adce4716479f3ad324a3bd203679cfa","tid":2125973,"uid":285195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T14:30:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/gelekchodar/photos/a.456970247752745/3064037497045994/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgelekchodar%2Fphotos%2Fa.456970247752745%2F3064037497045994%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=OqPbpPrVkTbcBhMc%2F4HaLmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=67043a50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/gelekchodar/photos/a.456970247752745/3064037497045994/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：王喜<br />\n<br />\n24小時內，無官出嚟舉證辟謠的<br />\n話，即認證以下描述的是事實囉。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vwjPFSS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvwjPFSS.jpg&h=399d91cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n喺航空界同機場做左20年嘅人話你知。。。 *Forward俾多啲人知please... 我眼見好多人喺機場自動自覺去呢部機俾政府/機管局收集你嘅資料。包括你個樣，護照/回鄉證資料，機票資料。 其實，呢部機唔係政府，係機管局用黎收集所謂統計數據。你可以去返人手櫃位，話唔願意被收集，佢(AVSECO, 唔係政府人員) 就用人眼望下你個樣，機票，同passport/回鄉證，就算。咁樣政府/機管局 就唔知你去邊同埋你&quot;最新&quot;個樣係點。 啲AVSECO叫你行埋去嗰部機做，就話&quot;我唔想被收集&quot;就得。有晒terms講可以拒絕收集用返人手幫助。 點解呢部機擺喺禁區外？ 咪就係因為呢部機唔係出入境要求嘅一部份囉！佢扮到你一定要俾佢scan咁。仲有，呢部機唔係由入境處睇，只係由扮紀律部隊嘅AVSECO(機場保安) 負責。 傻的先會自願俾佢收集。 **幫手forward"},{"pid":"f0d114329d8bf206ba53cd8c03d05059f869392d","tid":2125973,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T14:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce7d3770475e7d512a0fed4c83d466dddccf148","tid":2125973,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T14:34:25.000Z","